28:48.333 --> 28:51.000
Uh, about that burglary..

28:52.100 --> 28:54.100
What was taken?

28:54.166 --> 28:56.566
I'm not sure.

28:56.633 --> 28:58.733
Why don't we check the bedroom?

29:02.633 --> 29:04.600
There is no burglary,
is there, Tania?

29:06.166 --> 29:08.300
'Are you trying to seduce me?'

29:19.666 --> 29:21.700
Aren't you coming to bed?

29:21.766 --> 29:23.433
Uh, in a minute.

29:23.500 --> 29:25.933
I don't think
I can wait that long.

29:45.166 --> 29:47.300
What's gotten into you?

29:47.366 --> 29:49.400
Shh.

29:49.466 --> 29:50.933
Don't talk.

29:52.200 --> 29:53.633
Come here.

30:03.500 --> 30:05.500
Would you like to help, David?

30:55.466 --> 30:56.733
Good morning.

31:00.033 --> 31:02.266
What's the matter?
What did I say?

31:02.333 --> 31:03.500
I love your attitude.

31:03.566 --> 31:05.433
It's so cavalier.

31:05.500 --> 31:07.766
- What are you talking about?
- Don't touch me.

31:07.833 --> 31:10.333
