31:27.466 --> 31:28.766
Hello?

31:28.833 --> 31:30.500
'Yeah, Mr. Lewis,
this is Captain Shaw'

31:30.566 --> 31:31.833
'over at the police department.'

31:31.900 --> 31:32.900
Yes.

31:32.966 --> 31:34.166
'I'm sorry to bother you,
Mr. Lewis'

31:34.233 --> 31:36.133
'but, uh,
I'm trying to determine'

31:36.200 --> 31:37.366
'the whereabouts
of one of my men.'

31:37.433 --> 31:39.000
'Detective Nick Charles.'

31:40.933 --> 31:44.166
Nick Charles, Springwood PD.

31:44.233 --> 31:46.166
'He was last seen just prior
to answering'

31:46.233 --> 31:47.766
'a call at your address.'

31:47.833 --> 31:49.533
Mmm, you look like..

31:50.500 --> 31:52.433
...a man a woman can trust

31:54.166 --> 31:57.100
He, uh, he must've talked
to my wife.

32:00.633 --> 32:02.900
Uh, I'll-I'll talk to her

32:02.966 --> 32:05.500
and-and-and get back to you
as soon as I can, captain.

32:05.566 --> 32:07.633
'Alright, now, I appreciate it,
Mr. Lewis.'

32:07.700 --> 32:08.800
'So long now.'

32:08.866 --> 32:09.833
Right.

32:39.600 --> 32:41.866
"Tania rose with the sun.

32:41.933 --> 32:43.866
