in a row she's missed.

33:16.366 --> 33:18.433
What-what do you mean
missed two sessions?

33:18.500 --> 33:20.666
She saw you yesterday,
didn't she?

33:20.733 --> 33:22.300
She wasn't here when I came.

33:22.366 --> 33:25.366
I-I waited the entire hour.
She never showed.

33:25.433 --> 33:27.066
Doctor, has-has Kim
ever talked to you

33:27.133 --> 33:28.466
about the novel she's writing?

33:28.533 --> 33:29.966
Nothing other than just say that

33:30.033 --> 33:31.500
it was going well.

33:31.566 --> 33:34.900
That she was really getting into
the head of the main character.

33:34.966 --> 33:37.900
Yes, literally gotten into
the head of the main character.

33:37.966 --> 33:40.066
I think she's assumed
the personality of Tania

33:40.133 --> 33:41.566
the heroine of her novel.

33:41.633 --> 33:43.733
David, you're-you're-you'r
on the wrong track.

33:43.800 --> 33:45.500
Listen to me,
listen to me, this book

33:45.566 --> 33:49.266
started out as a,
a light romantic adventure

33:49.333 --> 33:50.933
Since the assault,
it's-it's turned

33:51.000 --> 33:52.733
into a macabre killing spree.

33:52.800 --> 33:55.166
Her mood has grown darker,
but it seems only natural

33:55.233 --> 33:57.666
that her fiction
reflect those changes.

33:57.733 --> 33:59.966
Doctor, she is losing
touch with reality.

34:00.033 --> 34:02.800
She's living in a fantasy world.

34:02.866 --> 34:05.066
Can you tell me anything that
you, you two have talked about?

34:05.133 --> 34:07.033
