information.

34:07.100 --> 34:08.733
'Even for husbands.'

34:09.866 --> 34:11.000
'I gotta go back to the office.'

34:11.066 --> 34:13.633
Uh, when Kim comes in,
have her give me a call.

34:34.533 --> 34:36.866
"Tania thought
about the doctor.

34:36.933 --> 34:39.566
"In fact, she thought
about him a lot.

34:39.633 --> 34:41.533
"She knew she wanted him.

34:41.600 --> 34:44.100
