towards your husband?

34:51.733 --> 34:54.033
Because he's a sick pervert,
that's why.

34:55.033 --> 34:56.500
Didn't he tell you
what he made me do?

34:59.066 --> 35:01.100
Why don't you tell me?

35:04.433 --> 35:08.733
Doctor...do you like to listen
to girls talk dirty?

35:11.500 --> 35:13.000
I thought so.

35:13.066 --> 35:15.200
Just as horny as the next guy,
aren't you?

35:17.833 --> 35:21.333
Oh, doctor.
You're make me feel so hot

35:23.633 --> 35:25.433
I can feel your eyes.

35:25.500 --> 35:27.700
And they see
right through my clothes.

35:29.166 --> 35:32.133
