38:47.033 --> 38:48.066
Yes.

38:48.133 --> 38:49.733
I can't let you do that.

38:49.800 --> 38:52.000
And what if you get caught
and you go to prison?

38:52.066 --> 38:54.000
I can't live with the idea
of you behind bars.

38:54.066 --> 38:55.733
There's no other way.

38:57.566 --> 38:58.833
Yes, there is.

39:00.133 --> 39:01.633
