40:08.766 --> 40:10.366
Oh, you know,
on-on second thought

40:10.433 --> 40:12.433
maybe I will have some honey.

40:12.500 --> 40:14.533
It's, uh,
on that shelf back there.

40:34.066 --> 40:35.200
