the confidential relationship

41:13.666 --> 41:15.300
between a doctor and a patient.

41:18.500 --> 41:20.633
'Yes, David, that's all
I can tell you.'

41:23.366 --> 41:26.433
What about the relationshi
between a husband and wife

41:29.266 --> 41:32.633
You don't seem to have a problem
