what you're talking about.

41:34.333 --> 41:36.300
You see, I know
what's been going on

41:36.366 --> 41:37.666
with you and Kim.

41:37.733 --> 41:38.666
'David--'

41:38.733 --> 41:39.700
And I know that you tried

41:39.766 --> 41:41.500
