41:41.566 --> 41:45.300
That's why...I switched
cups with you.

41:45.366 --> 41:48.100
D-D-David, what in God's name
are you talking ab..

42:13.800 --> 42:14.933
Hello, David.

42:15.600 --> 42:16.766
