42:27.300 --> 42:29.933
I warned you not to,
but you went against my wishes.

42:31.300 --> 42:34.100
That's why I planted
those buttons under the table.

42:34.166 --> 42:35.766
Unfortunately for you

42:35.833 --> 42:37.200
I rewrote the last chapter

42:38.533 --> 42:41.133
Tania decided not to seduc
her psychiatrist.

42:42.166 --> 42:43.533
You didn't have an affair
with him?

42:44.400 --> 42:45.800
Tania realized she could get rid

42:45.866 --> 42:48.566
of both of her problems
at the same time.

42:48.633 --> 42:51.533
Her nosy shrink
and her contemptible husband.

42:52.733 --> 42:57.033
So she lined...
both cups with poison.

42:57.100 --> 43:00.800
One fast acting, producing a
virtually instantaneous death.

43:00.866 --> 43:04.100
The other one...a bit slower.

43:04.166 --> 43:06.400
So I could have the privilege
of watching you die.

43:07.500 --> 43:09.400
The detective..

43:09.466 --> 43:11.966
...you murdered him too, you..

43:15.233 --> 43:17.466
Oh, I hope you don't mind
if I watch?

43:17.533 --> 43:20.066
Just some research
on this method of poisoning.

43:20.133 --> 43:23.000
See, what's supposed
to happen first is..

43:23.066 --> 43:24.866
...the blood vessels
in your lungs contract

43:24.933 --> 43:26.333
cutting off the oxygen
to your brain

43:26.400 --> 43:28.100
and sending you
into cardiac arrest.

43:37.500 --> 43:39.233
Have you lost control
of your bowels yet?

43:42.766 --> 43:45.100
Gee, I didn't realize
it would last this long.

43:47.300 --> 43:48.500
Good bye, David.

43:49.633 --> 43:50.700
'That sick mind of yours'

43:50.766 --> 43:52.533
'is about to destroy itself.'

44:32.866 --> 44:35.666
Pretty juicy stuff, huh?

44:37.100 --> 44:38.600
I guess this just goes to show

44:38.666 --> 44:41.700
you don't have to be crazy
to be a good writer..

44:42.633 --> 44:44.166
